title: The Viz - Hand Picked And Sorted
description:
Hey folks,

Extremely hard to find on the net, here are some back issues of the amazingly funny, irreverent comic. Known and loved in the U.K.

Featuring such classic characters as:
Roger Mellie
Buster Gonad and his unfeasibly large testicles
Millie Tant
Sid the Sexist
Spoilt Bastard
The Fat Slags
etc etc

Hand sorted from around 100 back issues into .cbz files for each main character, with other .cbz files for ads, features and one off comic strips.

Maximised for enhanced readability.

You can see a complete list here: bayimg.com/LagIIaafI

Enjoy.
